    "content": "Let us read\nWhen I meet someone in \nthe afternoon, I say ‘Good \nafternoon’.\nWhen I meet someone in \nthe morning, I say ‘Good \nmorning’.\nWhen I go to bed, I say ‘Good \nnight’.\nWhen I meet someone in \nthe evening, I say ‘Good \nevening’.\nNote to the teacher\n• Ask the children how they greet others in their mother tongue."
