    "content": "16\nMridang\nA. Match the pictures with the sentences.\nNote to the teacher\n• Read the sentences aloud for the children.\n• Ensure that the children learn the action words such as— \ncombing, eating, seeing, saying, hearing.\nLet us write\nI comb my hair.\nI see my teacher.\nI eat my food.\nI hear the bell ring.\nI walk to school.\nI play football."
