    "content": "17\nMridang\nA. Write these letters\nSing the ABC song again.\nNote to the teacher\n• Before doing the above exercise, make letter flash \ncards to indicate directions when tracing the letters.\nLet us write\nI\nJ\nK\nLl\nN n\nMm\nP\nO o\nG\nH"
