    "id": "e1168",
    "subject": "English",
    "page": 125,
    "chapter": "Unit 4 \nSeasons",
    "content": "110 Mridang\nWinter\nPrithvi has gone to Shimla. It is cold there. What is Prithvi \nwearing? What things do you see in the picture?\nMonsoon\nCircle the words you see in the picture.\nraindrops\nboat\nmat\npot\nhouse\nroses\nsun\npuddle\nmud\ncat\numbrella"
