    "chapter": "Unit 4 \nSeasons",
    "content": "111\nMridang\nA. Look at the pictures. Say the names of the clothes \nwe wear.\nsari\ndhoti-kurta\nshirt\ncap\nfrock\npants\nLet us speak\nsalwar suit\nt-shirt\nlungi-\nangavastram"
