    "page": 129,
    "chapter": "Pitter Patter",
    "content": "114 Mridang\nWrite down the words that come to your mind when you say \nsummer, winter or monsoon.\nA few words have been written for you.\ncold\nwoolen cap\nholidays\nSummer\numbrella\nclouds\ncolourful\nnew leaves\nSpring\nWinter\nMonsoon\nhot\nLet us write"
