    "content": "A Visit to an Amusement Park\nA group of children visited an amusement park.\nHow Many Times?\n11\nWow! 2 of us can sit \non the horse. I will \nsit with my friend.\nThe total \nchildren are\n2 + 2 + 2 + 2 = \n3 of us can sit in \na toy train. We all \nwill sit together.\nThere are 3 bogies. 3 + 3 + 3 = \nTotal \n children can sit in 3 bogies.\n of us can sit on the horse swing altogether."
